            <P><font face="Arial" size="4"><b> 1.1 - Referral Compliance (w/Reg)</b></font></P>
    </td>        
 </tr>			
 <tr>
        <td><br>
			The referral compliance report allows clients to enter hospital death data (obtained from medical record review or other communication by the procurement agency and each individual hospital) on-line over the Internet.  The actual hospital deaths entered by the procurement agency are then compared to the number of referrals received by Statline and referral compliance (%) is calculated.  The total number of donors registered with the DMV or Donor Registry is also listed.
